{"nodes": [{"id": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1", "label": "P9.1 \u2014 N2 drift-slowdown bake-off", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase9/exp1/experiment-1.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1_n2_struck", "label": "N2 struck \u2014 no read-side lever grips the drift", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase9/exp1/experiment-1.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The last open Stage-2 decision-record knob (N2, a drift-slowdown lever) resolves standby\u2192struck: neither EMA-view nor LLRD-rate sleeps sparser or improves worst-point BWT than no-N2; EMA-view actively worsens BWT via a train/eval frame mismatch. Because P9.0 showed the drift is rotation-only and the cadence already tracks it, there is no residual drift left for N2 to slow."}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1_ema_view_arm", "label": "EMA-view \u2014 the doubly-grounded N2 default (struck)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase9/exp1/experiment-1.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A stateful per-tap EMA applied read-side to the features the namer reads (SCFF untouched); worsens worst-point BWT (\u22120.383/\u22120.344 vs no-N2's \u22120.317) because subtracting a time-varying birth-relative accumulator creates a train/eval frame mismatch \u2014 the namer consolidates in a frame the eval has already moved past."}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1_llrd_rate_arm", "label": "LLRD-rate \u2014 the rate-only secondary N2 arm (struck, no lever)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase9/exp1/experiment-1.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A LLRDCell subclass slowing only the late-read layers' SCFF update rate (early/mid taps guarded unmoved at 0.00 \u2014 no Stage-1 reopen); neither sparsens the sleep cadence nor improves worst-BWT (within noise vs no-N2) \u2014 a null lever on drift that is already rotation-only and already tracked."}], "edges": [{"source": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp0_experiment_0", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase9/exp1/experiment-1.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1_n2_struck", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase9/exp1/experiment-1.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1_ema_view_arm", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase9/exp1/experiment-1.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1_llrd_rate_arm", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase9/exp1/experiment-1.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp0_experiment_0_destruction_curve", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1_n2_struck", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase9/exp1/experiment-1.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase9_exp1_experiment_1_n2_struck", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp3_experiment_3_grid8_cadence", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "con